Package dev.galasa.framework.spi

Enum Class DssPropertyKeyRunNameSuffix

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<DssPropertyKeyRunNameSuffix>
dev.galasa.framework.spi.DssPropertyKeyRunNameSuffix
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<DssPropertyKeyRunNameSuffix>, Constable
public enum DssPropertyKeyRunNameSuffix extends Enum<DssPropertyKeyRunNameSuffix>
An enum of Dss property suffixes pertaining to a single run. These are used by the Galasa framework. The general format of the whole dss key is "run.{runName}.{suffix}" This is a list of all the suffixes used.
